Publications

Here you can search for all publications that are linked to the Department of Archaeology and Classical Studies.

You can search by free text, filter by type of publication and year period, and sort them by year, author and title. The publications are linked to the university's publication database DiVA, where you can see all information about the publication and any full-text version. Search for the names of the various units to further filter the search results: Ancient culture and social life; Archaeology; Archaeological Research Laboratory; Numismatic research group; Osteoarchaeological Research Laboratory.
